# Derived from qwen2.5:7b-instruct with an enlarged context window, evaluated as a
# tool-calling retriever (RET-OLL) alternative to llama3.1:8b, which fabricated tool
# calls under our harness (see reports/findings-retriever-prompt-revision.md).
#
# WHY num_ctx: same as the llama3.1 derived model — Ollama's default context (~2-4K)
# truncates the ~9K-token index tree, so the retriever would navigate a half-read index.
# 32768 fits the structure dump + fetched page content + the tool-calling conversation.
#
# BUILD (once per machine):
#   ollama create qwen2.5-7b-instruct-ctx32k -f config/ollama/qwen2.5-7b-instruct-ctx32k.Modelfile
#
# USE:
#   retriever (RET-OLL):  ollama_chat/qwen2.5-7b-instruct-ctx32k
FROM qwen2.5:7b-instruct
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768
